code: @Override public BootstrapCheckResult check(BootstrapContext context) {     if (XPackSettings.TRANSPORT_SSL_ENABLED.get(context.settings()) == false) {         License license = LicenseService.getLicense(context.metaData()).         if (license != null && license.isProductionLicense()) {             return BootstrapCheckResult.failure("Transport SSL must be enabled for setups with production licenses. Please set " + "[xpack.security.transport.ssl.enabled] to [true] or disable security by setting [xpack.security.enabled] " + "to [false]").         }     }     return BootstrapCheckResult.success(). }
